  "name": "RPlog_The_Crypts_of_Ord_Trasi",
  "title": "The Crypts of Ord Trasi",
  "summary": "Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin leads a party including his captive Jedi Johanna, the pilot Dareus, and the Mandalorian Master Sergeant Cantrell deep into the ancient crypts of Ord Trasi, guided by a holocron toward the tomb of his Sith ancestor Davin Keldan. The treacherous caverns nearly claim Dareus and Cantrell when a floor collapses, but the troopers haul them to safety and the group leaps the gap to reach the sealed tomb doors. Johanna uses telekinesis to force the doors open, only for the tomb to be revealed utterly empty, its secrets either looted over a thousand years or never there at all. Enraged, Danik strikes Johanna and demands she unlock the holocron, threatening her son Etiel, until a swarm of vicious Terentatek Sithspawn bursts through the ceiling. As the creatures slaughter stormtroopers, Danik orders a full retreat and Dareus radios the ship to prep for an emergency evacuation, the party fleeing the temple empty-handed.",
